"The security of your organisation doesn't just depend on eliminating the vulnerabilities from your networks and your devices. In this highly interconnected world, your weakest point might be the other organisations with which you work, such as suppliers and partners. But how do you assess the risk of another organisation? As Jasson Casey, CTO at SecurityScorecard, explains in this interview, firms have difficulty judging their own risk. When it comes to analysing others, they definitely need help."
